----------
  About:
----------

 - easily encrypt your data using AES, ARC2, Blowfish, CAST, DES3 or RSA then encode the result
    in a printable form, using Base64, Base32, HEX, Quopri, string escape, UU, XML or Json;
 - the resulted string can be sent on e-mail as text, saved as XML, Json or UU, or can be
    transformed into a little PNG image;
 - website : http://scrambled-egg.googlecode.com

