-----------------
  Requirements:
-----------------
 * Python 2.6/2.7. Scrambled-Egg is written in Python 2.7. (www.python.org)
 * Python Crypto. Data is crypted in AES, Blowfish, DES3, etc. (www.pycrypto.org)
 * PyQt4. Graphical user interface and PNG image with Qt. (www.riverbankcomputing.co.uk/software/pyqt)

---------------
  How to use:
---------------
 * Graphical user interface can be accesed by opening "scrambled_egg.py" directly.
 * The text must be written in the left text-box.
 * In order to access Scrambled-Egg class, all you have to do is : "import scrambled_egg".
 * Tested on Windows, Ubuntu and OpenSUSE.

---------------------------------
  Known Issues and Limitations:
---------------------------------
 * Don't use Quopri Codec with binary files (images, music, Doc/Xls files, executables).
    The result after decoding might be differend from the original file !!
 * Base32 Codec is VERY slow, so never use it for large files.
 * RSA encryption is VERY slow, so never use it for large files.
    RSA is very strong encryption, you should only use it for small pieces of text.
 * The GUI will freeze for a looong time if you try to encrypt/ decrypt more than
    200.000-300.000 characters !

---------------
  What's new:
---------------
 * Version 0.4 brings the following changes :
    - added RSA encryption and Json encoding. RSA should only be used for small text messages;
    - password enhancement. The key is derived from original password making the encryption stronger;
    - drag & drop your text in the left area.

 * Version 0.3 brings the following changes :
    - better encryption. All modes use CBC;
    - images resulted from HEX codec are about 25-33% smaller than images resulted from Base64/32;
    - checkbox to show HTML;
    - better testing. The program is stable. Tested on hundreds of files
      (images, music, office documents, executables);
    - the GUI looks nicer.

 * Version 0.2 brings quite some changes :
    - a lot of bug fixes;
    - stability obtained after MASSIVE testing;
    - all operations are faster;
    - added ARC2 encryption, Base32 and XML encodings;
    - import and export operations directly from GUI;
    - checkbox to show and hide pre/enc/post tags in resulted text.

